cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper is about parallel training of Deep Neural Networks (DNN) on multi-GPU platforms. The most relevant sub-category is likely to be cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on improving the training process of DNNs. Other possible sub-categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these areas are also relevant to the topic of parallel DNN training.
